{"tid":370032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵接連故障　港鐵主席籲市民諒解：機械會壞　大家對港鐵要公平","createTime":"2017-08-22T18:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T02:50:54.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e215851bd43d51f4ad57ecc9fd55941db47bba","tid":370032,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170822/s00001/1503392492933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170822%2Fs00001%2F1503392492933&d=wdi%2FwlnpTPpwbaPXYtwCwDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b387e58a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170822%2Fs00001%2F1503392492933&h=0f180818\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170822/s00001/1503392492933</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170822/s00001/5bf1b51ffbc6dbf51877a83a744b7334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170822%2Fs00001%2F5bf1b51ffbc6dbf51877a83a744b7334.jpg&h=9020ec02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日港鐵接二連三信號故障，港鐵主席馬時亨說，機械是會壞的，大家對港鐵要公平，亦不能保證日後沒有延誤。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨出席活動後介紹港鐵在10月1、2兩日推優惠，慶祝香港回歸20周年。兩日間市民使用成人八達通乘搭港鐵可享小童優惠，即是大約半價，小童、傷殘人士及長者則可以1元乘港鐵。<br />\n<br />\n現場記者問馬時亨港鐵接連故障，推出這等優惠是否「小恩小惠」，他回應時重申港鐵每年花80億元維修，預料維修費仍會增加，而港鐵在世界來說，服務水平非常高，希望市民原諒及諒解，又道「機械是會壞的」，大家對港鐵要公平，不能保證日後沒有延誤。<br />\n<br />\n他又說自己明白市民遇上延誤會不開心，港鐵亦不想見到發生延誤，若有延誤，同事亦會盡快修補。"},{"pid":"3f733cc9504e77be3c709c6bbecfadf7f8777147","tid":370032,"uid":44673,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，成撚日買撚堆啲大陸車唔壞就奇啦"},{"pid":"bd96e5e16e2ae8ed6f0d901d786f9ea6f582e05e","tid":370032,"uid":3457,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:50:34.000Z","msg":"咁你地有冇對市民公平呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"e9d0d680c176508432d426b2be